desc_short	-----								Infinity Wars is a genuine free-to-play trading card game. Play with fully animated cards in 3D battlefields, and assemble decks from over 800 cards and 8 stylized factions. Explore the strategic depth of simultaneous gameplay and compete in a number of PvP game modes and an extensive PvE campaign.							
